{"tid":890044,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[都係贏]習近平：中國將降低關稅　提升通關便利","createTime":"2018-11-05T04:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T21:03:43.000Z","uid":57424,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aba4d359fc610388e0f24be9fe982b3d0f82047d","tid":890044,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=326145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D326145&d=Cn2FJn9iyZyQjV4k33VECp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=2847a73d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D326145&h=ea7ca5cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=326145</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中國國際進口博覽會開幕，國家主席習近平發表主旨演講，他稱進博會是中國對外開放市場的重大舉措，中國會持續放寬市場准入。<br />\n<br />\n習近平呼籲各國應堅持開放融通，拓展開放互利空間。他稱中國將降低關稅，提升通關便利，對內將激發進口潛力，刺激中高端消費。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱要發揮上海等地區對外開放的重要作用，包括上交所會設立科創板，並進行註冊制試點。<br />\n<br />\n進博會一連六日在上海國家會展中心舉行，是全球第一個以進口為主題的國家級展覽會，吸引超過170個國家及地區，逾三千間企業參加，其間會有100多項新產品及技術公布<br />\n<br />\n減關稅係因為<strong>提升通關便利，對內將激發進口潛力，刺激中高端消費。</strong><br />\n<br />\n支那狗, 你有得減入息稅, 同消費稅, 多謝侵侵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fe76b80d5e6e9c79a186524d0f253a1607ec9a","tid":890044,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:24:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=326129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D326129&d=Cn2FJn9iyZyQjV4k33VECp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=77172408\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D326129&h=2feaefd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=326129</a><br />\n<br />\n工信部擬推出減稅降費等政策支持中小企發展<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中國工信部計劃推出減稅降費等政策措施，支持中小企發展。<br />\n<br />\n工信部部長苗圩表示，將抓緊制定推出進一步支持中小企業發展的政策措施，包括減稅降費，以解決中小企業融資難融資貴的問題，搭建為中小企業服務的公共平台，協調各省份加強對中小企業發展的政策支持力度等。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，工信部近年來在相對封閉的移動通訊轉售業務和電訊市場開放方面進行了一些嘗試，取得了一定成效，下一步工信部將進一步放寬市場準入，鼓勵民間資本進入電訊和軍工領域。"},{"pid":"fa9c7f44aa2fa53b90231014ba36aaa72a86c10f","tid":890044,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16404d946fdde81b014a4c24655c8f2bb0b3b9e3","tid":890044,"uid":57424,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"姐係話之前收鳩你重稅阻鳩你班賤民發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家減下稅, 又要感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做支那人真係好撚忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29900b203fdd42ae6dbb9163ca89eef47bff8870","tid":890044,"uid":191926,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"聽下先算<br />\n<br />\n支共堆友只係玩緊用時間換空間"},{"pid":"b68ae0e9a07f8bde324c33cbba6f50d6cbc15191","tid":890044,"uid":126100,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:26:59.000Z","msg":"陰D陰D投降，再搵黨媒吹捧下同歪曲事實，<br />\n<br />\n中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e0e67da1ea81f898a16472f230126fe33b6406","tid":890044,"uid":192589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"上面成班傻西專家又開始自high"},{"pid":"560a659008577a88544671943080b4e816ec4345","tid":890044,"uid":173631,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">倪匡：信妓女明碼實價，也不要信共產黨反口覆舌，不知羞恥為何物</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535618142_5ba6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2F